    "body": "If the fix for SOL-008 is accepted (https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/pull/3348), the error message will be different, and much shorter for values over 1E1232. For 1E1232, the error message length is approximately 1586 bytes. The new error message will be along the lines of:\r\n\r\n```\r\nbiginttest.sol:6:11: Error: Invalid literal value.\r\n        c=1E1233;\r\n          ^----^\r\n```",
